	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Dwedit wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Besides the APU and Cartridge, what can create IRQs?  Can the expansion port generate them?</div>
<br />
<br />Yes.  To be specific, hardware connected to the expansion port can generate them.  I'd expect it's a wired-or circuit, so any number of devices can generate IRQs using the same pin.
<br />
<br />I believe there's also a "frame IRQ", I don't know much about it because it seemed totally useless.  I don't know if that's from the APU or what, there's not much else it could come from.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
